self._table_name = 'animal'
self.animal = Table(self._table_name, self.metadata, Column('animal_name',
    String(40), nullable=False, primary_key=True), Column('animal_desc',
    String(255), nullable=False), Column('animal_age', Integer, nullable=
    False), CheckConstraint('animal_age < 100'))
self._table = self.animal
return self._table
